{"tid":2004494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[DW] 五分之一的中國口罩「沒法用」 真的嗎？","createTime":"2020-05-06T13:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T13:32:57.000Z","uid":179729,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"770676c99fbf11122996152405054fc21bfc1059","tid":2004494,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.dw.com/image/53053776_303.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fimage%2F53053776_303.jpg&h=9f300a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">德國發行量最大的報紙媒體《圖片報》本週一發表報導題為&quot;五分之一的中國口罩沒法用！&quot;（Jede 5. China Maske ist unbrauchbar）的文章，援引德國衛生部一位發言人的表態報導稱：自從新冠疫情爆發以來，德國聯邦政府已經為醫院以及診所從中國購買了超過1億只口罩。&quot;根據衛生部的推斷，大約有20%的口罩不符合標準&quot;。《圖片報》就此斷定稱：&quot;也就是說這些口罩根本無法醫用。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n該部的發言人瑙博爾（Teresa Nauber）證實：確實有大約20%來自中國的口罩&quot;與標準不符&quot;。但她明確指出：&quot;這不意味著這些口罩無法醫用。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://dw.com/p/3bqbl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw.com%2Fp%2F3bqbl&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=9b050cf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://dw.com/p/3bqbl</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/876314039537907\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdw.chinese.traditional%2Fposts%2F876314039537907&d=HVlUx73Us%2FxglV2o%2BMpWBSK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=bf34faf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dw.chinese.traditional/posts/876314039537907</a>"},{"pid":"8847487ac7b766407ec4ef9f52fe34aea602562b","tid":2004494,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個80%來自台灣</span>"},{"pid":"af5ee6f7fab28f648f61e2f1bacdd4c4c997994e","tid":2004494,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply